Package Entity

package Entity
  • Class
    Description
    Admin
    Entity Class representing an Admin account Sub Class of a person
    Booking
    Entity Class representing a Booking
    Customer
    Entity Class representing a Customer A subclass inheriting from Person super class
    Holiday
    Entity Class representing a Holiday For booking tickets, when the showschedule date coincides with a holiday prices would be affected
    Movie
    Entity Class representing a Movie A particular Movie Class contains all of the details about a movie, the enums of movieStatus and ageAdvisory, as well as take down and release Dates(for computation of End of Show, Preview, Coming Soon Status)
    MovieEnums
    An Class Containing the various enum Classes catering to the configuration of a particular movie
    MovieEnums.AgeAdvisory
    This enum class shows the AgeAdvisory category of a movie to be chosen.
    MovieEnums.MovieStatus
    This enum class shows the Status of the movie to be Chosen
    Person
    Entity Class representing a Person For MovieGoer and Admin Sub-classes
    Review
    Entity Class representing a Review the reviews must be tagged to a particular movie
    Seat
    Entity Class representing a Particular Seat in a ShowSchedule includes methods to print the layout of EACH seat, be it normal seats or couple seats
    ShowSchedule
    Entity Class representing a ShowSchedule A particular ShowSchedule contains all of the Seat Classes, and associates with Movie and Theatre Class to extract the movie and theatre details
    SystemSettings
    Entity Class representing a SystemSetting by the Admin user
    Theatre
    Entity Class representing a Theatre A Theatre can be configured according to 3D, theatreclass, cineplex, location and code.
    TheatreEnums
    An Class Containing the various enum Classes catering to the settings of the theatre
    TheatreEnums.CinemaLocation
    This enum class shows the locations of the theatres to be chosen
    TheatreEnums.Cineplex
    This enum class shows the cineplex brand to be chosen
    TheatreEnums.TheatreClass
    This enum class shows the classes of the theatres to be chosen
